```

#### Fitting a PLS-QDA

```julia
mod = plsqda(nlv = 25)
fit!(mod, Xtrain, ytrain)
pred = predict(mod, Xtest).pred
errp(pred, ytest)
```

#### Confusion matrixÂ²

